                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570223-33-off186 t17570223-33-crimeloc189"></join>, and the prisoner was my <rs id="t17570223-33-deflabel190" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570223-33-defend376 t17570223-33-deflabel190"></join>. My other servant, 
               <persName id="t17570223-33-person380">
